Title: Spongebob Sharkpants Backpack
Body (HTML):
This season we are proud to bring you a very special collaboration, with a very well known individual. He lives in a pineapple under the sea, absorbant and yellow and porous is he; If nautical nonsense is something you wish, then drop on the deck and flop like a fish. Ladies and gentlemen, we bring you, the Sprayground x Spongebob Deluxe Backpack.


With a 360 degree print featuring an array of characters ranging from Spongebob, to Mr. Crabs, this bag puts a new spin on an iconic, underwater character. The front panel features a wide-eyed Spongebob face, affixed with Sprayground's iconic shark mouth. The side panels display the bodies of both Patrick and Mr. Crabs and the back panel features Sandy. The straps display Spongebob's socks, and the interior features spongebob yellow print with a Patrick pink back wall.
